Package api4kb.doc.annotation.stability

Annotation types in this package indicate source code stability.

See: Description

  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    Alpha
    Indicates that the annotated source code is in alpha state.
    Beta
    Indicates that the annotated source code is in beta state.

Package api4kb.doc.annotation.stability Description

Annotation types in this package indicate source code stability. They share a common package, because there is no type system for annotations.
